snippet.title: C-Dogs SDL gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
A short gameplay trailer of the overhead run-and-gun, C-Dogs SDL.

Free download available for PC (Windows, Linux, macOS) and GCW-Zero handheld.

C-Dogs SDL is open source, and based on the classic DOS game C-Dogs.

https://github.com/cxong/cdogs-sdl

Music by dragor: https://soundcloud.com/dragorworks/phuture-dragor-remix-1
